description: Wondering if it's a good day for your motorcycle? Just ask Motorcycle forecast! Please note, decisions to buy, own, or ride a motorcycle should not be made based on the output of this Skill. It is intended only to bring a smile to the face of motorcycle owners and provide some enjoyment every now and then.
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask Motorcycle Forecast if today is a good day for a motorcycle
name: Motorcycle Forecast
